#

Classic Potato Salad

35 min
$10.99
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

EggsSoy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

SaladSide DishComfort Food

Description

A creamy, tangy potato salad that's perfect for picnics and barbecues!

Ingredients

  • yukon gold potatoes: 2 pounds
  • mayonnaise: 1 cup
  • dijon mustard: 2 tablespoons
  • celery: 1 cup, diced
  • red onion: 1/2 cup, diced
  • hard-boiled eggs: 4, chopped
  • pickles: 1/2 cup, diced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
